In current dryers, when we run the dryer (ex: drying clothes) we don't know when the clothes will be dried.
Therefore, the drying time is fixed (ex: 30 minutes, 40 minutes). Suppose, clothes only need 15 minutes to
be dried but the drying time is set to 30 minutes => waste of electricity. The goal is to implement AI solution
to optimization of drying time. The final result of this project will be a software product which uses AI
algorithm which can control 2 heatings and fans in dryer to optimization of drying time. Finally, customer
can deploy it to Raspberry PI in dryer.
